Get data from RosBris (DEPRECATED)

get_rosbris.Rd

Get data from RosBris (DEPRECATED)

Usage

get_rosbris(type, age = 1, initial = FALSE, lastyear = 2022)

Arguments

type

Character. Type of data for downloading. "m" = mortality, f = "ferility"

age

Numeric. Age group. 1 for one-year data, 5 for five-year data

initial

Logical. Do you want initial rosbris data? T for initial, F for 'long' format (default).

lastyear

Numeric. The last available year in rosbris (can be seen on the website). Default is 2022 (in 2023).

Value

List (if initial = TRUE) of dataframes: population and mortality/fertility data. Dataframe (if initial = FALSE) in long format.

References

Center for Demographic Research (2023). Russian Fertility and Mortality Database (Rosbris). URL
